rComments: When you receive your midterm, make sure to look it over! He make like 6 mistakes on mine and gave me a really low mark. I was an idiot and didn't look over it and I didn't realize the mistakes until it was to late. He's nice but I don't like having classes with him.

Great Guy. Sometimes the homework was actually impossible given the techniques we knew at that point but that didnt really matter because integral calculators exist. Hes very friendly. Once we brought our skates to school to go skating after and he asked us about hockey and Canada culture in general and was interested. Exams are easy with practice.
This guy cannot teach at all. He spends way too much time proving theorems, and he makes a huge amount of mistakes in examples. Avoid this prof at all costs!
